query:
SELECT cf.*, c.email, s.name as serviceName 
FROM customer_favorites cf 
JOIN customers c ON cf.customerId = c.id 
JOIN services s ON cf.serviceId = s.id 
ORDER BY cf.createdAt DESC LIMIT 10
